name: Separatio Synapsis # Magic Circle 04 #
description:
Next to light is born darkness. Next to right, is wrong. The splitting of the world made with the sword of consciousness can lead us to a separation from wholeness and life. Are you capable of surrendering to yourself?

Magic Circle is a collection based in the order of sacred geometry. Magic Circle is what means "Mandala". 

This piece was created based on my studies with Hydra Synth through a  generative code in SVG.

by @temenosart
